reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great lamps for the money!
reviews.reviewText: I highly recommend these lamps if you're looking for above average quality at an affordable price. They arrived packaged very well, were simple to assemble and look great on our living room end tables. The touch on / off feature is convenient and the charging port is an added plus. They even include 2 LED dimmable light bulbs. Look no further and buy these lamps! You'll be very satisfied.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This lamp is perfect for our 3 season room where we sometimes want a reading light on high level, a conversation light on medium and a low light in evening to relax. It looks great, love color and fact that controls are touch. Well packed. You need to assemble lamp shade and a bit of hardware but very easy to do! Great price, stylish and a quality product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Some assembly required.
reviews.reviewText: I was initially very upset thinking they messed up the order or shipped just the lamps and forgot the shades. Turns out everything came in one fairly small box. I was very surprised. For the lamps- they are beautiful. You have to put the metal light bulb part into the glass lamp part, its easy and not a big deal, the extra cord part fits into the metal light part. The lamp shade comes in three pieces and is a bit finicky. The canvas lamp shade has tiny little clips the rings fit into. You have to take the top ring (make sure the inside raised part is upside down) and clip the canvas shade around it. Then do the same with the bottom ring. Then Velcro the shades together. The rings fell off the clips a few times but eventually i got that velcro together, aligned and perfectly hidden. I love the lamps and the 3 dimmable stages are perfect. They look exactly like the picture. The brightness was just what I was looking for and the pricing was what good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The only reason I didn't give them a 5 star is because I don't care for the lamp shades. I wish they were a different color. They look cheap but other than that the glass color of the lamps is beautiful and I love how they are touch lamps and have USB ports on them. They are very handy and love the dimming option on them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. My old lamp broke and honestly I didn’t want to spend a fortune on new lamps. I read the reviews and they were actually pretty decent. I’m glad I got these. They came packaged so well!! I don’t know how they got the lamps in that little box! Anyway, straight out of the box was really simple to put together. You just have to screw the light into the post and that’s it’s! The lamp shade comes with it as well. So easy to clip onto the wire rim. They even supply the bulbs! Put the lampshade on screw it in place and you’re done! What I love is that it’s touch control. Tap it and it goes on, tap it again it goes off. It’s a three-way, which is really nice so you can control how bright or how dark you like it in the room. The glass is a grayish tint to it, which is really pretty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for older folks with limited reach
reviews.reviewText: I ordered two of these beautiful lamps for my retired parents and they work great. Touch them anywhere on the metal and you can change the light by 3 levels of brightness to turning it off and on. No more fumbling around in the dark trying to find the lamp switch under the shade and knocking it over. Charge your cell phone or other gadgets right from the bottom of the lamp. The shades were so easy to assemble and go wonderfully with the lamp itself. The lamps were very well packaged for shipping, no worries about breakage unless someone deliberately smashed the box, I don't think anything could happen to these lamps.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Could have been better
reviews.reviewText: The lamp is pretty, works just fine. The shade is not what as pictured, it is too small for a balanced look. The light bulb isn't bright enough for reading. Changed the bulb, bought new shade in larger size. I put this in the living room on a sofa back high table, works well there, if it had been on a side table I believe it would be too small. Like the touch switch and the charging ability for my remotes. After my changes, I like it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These surprised me. They look exactly like the picture. I had my concerns seeing the packaging. The shades are packaged unassembled and I wondered how that would work. The only trouble I ran into was fitting the socket on the lamp. It almost had too much cord to stuff in. But we managed it. These also come with bulbs which was really a nice surprise. Definitely worth purchasing.

These lamps are a great deal for the price! Not only are they stunning – they have 3 dimmable light settings with touch, and 2 USB charging ports at the base. So easy to assemble the lamp shades – I had them unboxed and plugged in within 10 minutes. Arrived in perfect condition and I would highly recommend.

Nice colour. Easy to put together but you really have to stuff the cord into the thing to get the light bulb part on. Looks very nice and like the fact that there’s no switch per se. just tap the lamp and it’s a tri-light. It has two USB ports on each lamp, which would be great if my gadgets still used USBs. Otherwise, I’m very happy with my purchase.

I wanted these lamps as they are tall and blue. The touch system takes a bit to get the lamp on and off but they look lovely Exactly what I was looking for. Lamp shades seem a bit cheap. But overall nice
